This paper is likely to belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category as it focuses on deep learning and proposes a new type of neuron. It could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as these fields are closely related to deep learning. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of quadratic networks in computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY), so these sub-categories are also likely.
